data.description: Beautiful, 3 sided brick ranch on a large .78 corner lot located in a sought after community within minutes of the Historic Covington Square and easy access to interstate.  This home features a foyer, large family room with fireplace with gas starter, separate dining, kitchen with breakfast room, walk in laundry with extra storage and pantry. Offers a large master suite on main level with sitting area and an ensuite with his and hers vanity, his and hers walk in closet, soaking tub and a tiled walk in shower. Bonus room upstairs could be 4th bedroom/media room/office or playroom.  Exterior has a private patio overlooking the nice large lot with a storage building for extra storage or to make into a he or she shed. Home has a new architectural roof installed 2/2024, new hot water heater, HVAC system replaced 10/2023, all carpets have been professionally cleaned and home is move in ready.
